### URLS ###

### ARCHIVES IN REPOSITORY ###

### GET ARCHIVE FILES LIST FETCHED FROM THE REPOSITORY URLS ABOVE AT HTTPS://MODEL-AI.COM
echo "-/- getting \"archives_list.csv\""
